Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.13,0:01:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.22,0:01:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 春香 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥小姐 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香 妳今天下午有雜誌的採訪對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為最近大家都不怎麼待在事務所裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我稍微有點寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡得坦率的替她們感到開心才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:01:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節目開始的時間到了
